column6:
A super fun place in super fun Austin!
Comfy, full bed, desk, and closet. Keyless entry, Wifi, full kitchen, livingroom, big yard. Sleeps 2, no pets.

Common area are shared with other Air b&b guests. On busline, near SoCo, downtown. #bestairbnb #uniqueairbnbrooms
